<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.400201>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Advertisement call of Leptolalax petrops sp. nov. (A) 30 s waveform of relative amplitude (Rel. amp.) over time for (i) holotype VNMN 2016 A. 06, (ii) paratype VNMN 2016 A. 11, (iii) paratype AMS R 184833, and (iv) AMS R 184832. (B) 2 s waveform and corresponding spectrogram of (i) holotype VNMN 2016 A. 06, (ii) paratype VNMN 2016 A. 11, (iii) paratype AMS R 184833, and (iv) paratype AMS R 184832. All recorded at 24.5 – 25.3 ° C." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/400201/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.400198>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Bayesian inference tree on ~ 570 bp fragment of the 16 S gene for Leptolalax petrops sp. nov., along with representatives of all Leptolalax species for which comparable sequences are available. Node support is indicated on branches as Bayesian posterior probabilities (upper half;> 0.95 = grey, 1 = black) and Maximum Likelihood support (lower;> 70 %, 100 = black)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/400198/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

